    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "AIR\nCALIFORNIA\nSystom Timetable\nEffective Sepiamber 1,1980\nONTARIO\nINTERNATIONA",
      "Ontario International Airport\nOntario is the convenient gateway to major cities\nin California, Nevada and Oregon on the airline\nthat wants everyone to fly.\nFrom Ontario International Airport Air Cali-\nfornia serves San Francisco, San Jose, Oakland,\nSacramento, Reno/Lake Tahoe, Las Vegas, Palm\nSprings and Portland.\nAir California serves more people with more\nflights from Ontario International Airport than\nany other airline.\nCall your Air California Travel Agent\nfor reservations.\nAIR\nCALIFORNIA"
    ],
